<h2 id="overview">Overview</h2>

<p>Having an integrated multicloud services management delivers:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Ultimate flexibility, freedom of choice and avoidance of vendor lock-in</li>
  <li>Simplified and delayered cloud and application management functions</li>
  <li>Consistency in monitoring, optimized data/workload placement, improved service management quality</li>
  <li>Reduced risk, enhanced resiliency, and improved reliability in your entire cloud operations</li>
  <li>Increased transparency, faster innovation and reduced cost through simplified governance</li>
</ul>

