<h2 id="security-operations-center-soc">Security Operations Center (SOC)</h2>

<p>The SOC proactively monitors, avoids outages, quickly troubleshoots and continuously improves through:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Single point of contact &amp; pane of glass view into Hybrid multicloud provider landscape which delivers application run/operate/service delivery with cost savings of up to 20%</li>
  <li>Integrated business services operations and management using proven SRE practices and AI-infused automation</li>
  <li>Embedded Hybrid IT Security assures data protection, resiliency, and compliance</li>
</ul>

