<hr />

<h2 id="security-cloud-framework">Security Cloud Framework</h2>

<p>Traditional security controls and infrastructure operational practices are changing to data and workload-centric cloud security policies, technologies, and practices. We approach this challenge by aligning security controls with the realities of your hybrid multicloud IT estate to:</p>

<ul>
  <li>Enforce Application security via DevSecOps practices</li>
  <li>Cloud Platform security</li>
  <li>Identification and planning for enterprise / regulatory specific controls / compliance / audits</li>
  <li>Data and Storage security and privacy</li>
  <li>Security threat monitoring</li>
  <li>Security incident management</li>
  <li>Business risk and compliance services</li>
</ul>

